        "cooked": "<p>Thank you very much for these clear and concise instructions!</p>\n<p>I see no menu item or preference for setting/changing a Signal PIN in the desktop software. I did however create a Signal PIN when the Android app asked me to, and I saved it in my password manager. The desktop software never asked me for it, the mobile app did of course. I assume I will be able to use this PIN for registering phone C, correct?</p>",
